description: Come celebrate with us! You won't want to miss this special performance as we welcome renowned violinist and beloved musician Jorja Fleezanis to perform accompanied by pianist Karl Paulnak, for our annual benefit concert!
title: Noe Valley Chamber Music Benefit Concert

description: This special event builds upon the success of a sold-out 2013 concert of Reich's music for 18 Musicians which, like this one, will be the culmination of a week-long residency by SFCMP musicians and Schick at the SF Conservatory of Music. Student musicians from the Conservatory will share the stage with SFCMP ensemble members in the performance of what has been called minimalism's first masterpiece, by musicologist K. Robert Schwarz.
title: SFCMP Presents Steve Reich's Drumming

description: VIP Package includes 30 min early entrance before doors, private 2 song acoustic set, meet and greet and pictures with the band, autographed limited edition tour poster, autographed VIP tour laminate ( this will not get you backstage), autographed CD of your choice, sponsor swag pack
title: Fortunate Youth's Fall with Friends VIP Package

description: Following the release of his third and highly praised EP, Kiss & Tell, on the London based Earnest Endeavors imprint, Bravo teamed up with fellow SF synth wizard Teeko to deliver the superb Starship Connection named after their seductive live band Starship Connection on the Frite Nite label.
title: The Starship Connection

description: Fans are encouraged to come to the show dressed up in Game of Thrones costumes. Kristian Nairn is a Northern Irish actor and musician. He is a successful DJ and has performed globally alongside acts such as the Scissor Sisters.
title: Rave of Thrones ft Kristian Nairn aka Hodor

description: Washed Out is Ernest Greene, a young guy from Georgia(via South Carolina) who makes bedroom synthpop that sounds blurred and woozily evocative, like someone smeared Vaseline all over an early OMD demo tape, then stayed up all night trying to recreate what they heard.
title: Washed Out DJ-set
